# Sinister LLC monorepo - global ignores

# Editor / launcher backup files (operator 2026-05-23: don't push .bak* to GitHub)
*.bak
*.bak-*

# Transient helper scripts emitted by forever-improve.ps1 -WithQualityLoop (auto-pruned >1d).
automations/_tmp/

# Seraphim QRNG provenance — runaway producer (1 file/30s; sibling sanctum sweep-loop
# has been stuck trying to add 1986+ files for hours without ever converging to commit).
# Operator review: if billing-audit trail needed in git, replace with a batched commit
# job (e.g. nightly rollup of the day's JSONs into one summary file). Added 2026-05-23
# by EVE on Sanctum during Phase-2 loop iteration 1 to break a multi-agent contention
# storm. Reversible: `git rm` this line if operator wants the per-event files committed.
_shared-memory/qrng-provenance/

# Custodian archive root — sanctum_custodian.py rotates oversized JSONL + quarantines
# oversized inbox JSON here. Never push archives to git; they exist for forensic
# recovery on disk. Added 2026-05-25 by sanctum-helper-A per operator directive
# "we should have a custdoian that cleans these things".
_shared-memory/_archive/

# Custodian-prevented: catch runaway inbox files (mojibake-explosion bugs created
# 141MB single-message JSON files that blocked git push). Added 2026-05-25.
_shared-memory/inbox/**/oversized-*.json

