# EVE.exe at repo root SHIPS so collaborators (Leo, fresh-clone) find it next to
# README.md without spelunking into automations/eve-launcher/dist/EVE/. Auto-synced
# by automations/verify-eve-features.ps1 -AutoRebuild -SyncMirror after every eve.py
# edit (per session-start-auto-update-propagation doctrine 2026-05-24).
# Operator hard-canonical 2026-05-25 ~03:30Z: "push the entire sanctum to github with
# the exe in the main folder where he can find it like read me".
!EVE.exe

# RKOJ source-only asset originals (large .bak / .webp masters); kept on
