# Nested per-project git repos under projects/ — these are junctions/clones of product
# repos owned by per-project agents (snap-emu, panel, kernel-apk, tiktok-emu). Sanctum
# must NOT pin them as gitlinks; lane discipline says each product repo pushes itself.
# Scaffold READMEs / non-source content at projects/<repo>/ root stays tracked.
projects/*/source/
projects/*/source/source/

# v15 (RKOJ-ELENO 2026-05-21): Sinister Forge source is REAL code (not a
# junction like the other project source/ dirs). Track it.
!projects/sinister-forge/source/
!projects/sinister-forge/source/**

# v16 (RKOJ-ELENO 2026-05-21): RKOJ source promoted to projects/rkoj/source/
# from tools/sinister-rkoj-qt/ — it is REAL code (PyQt6 native shell), not a
# junction. Track it. Build/dist/__pycache__ still ignored by the patterns
# higher up in this file.
!projects/rkoj/source/
!projects/rkoj/source/**
projects/rkoj/source/**/build/
projects/rkoj/source/**/dist/
projects/rkoj/source/**/__pycache__/
projects/rkoj/source/**/*.tmp
projects/rkoj/source/**/pyinstaller-*.log

# v18 (RKOJ-ELENO 2026-05-24): Sinister OS source is REAL code (ISO build scripts,
# EVE control daemon, branding artifacts) — not a junction. Track it. Build artifacts
# (ISOs / packages) go in projects/sinister-os/build/ which has its own .gitignore.
!projects/sinister-os/source/
!projects/sinister-os/source/**
projects/sinister-os/source/**/__pycache__/
projects/sinister-os/source/**/target/
projects/sinister-os/source/**/*.iso

# v19 (RKOJ-ELENO 2026-05-24): Sinister iMessage Bridge source is REAL code (bridge
# daemon, AppleScript wrappers, chat.db poller, CLI) — not a junction. Track it.
!projects/sinister-imessage-bridge/source/
!projects/sinister-imessage-bridge/source/**
projects/sinister-imessage-bridge/source/**/__pycache__/
projects/sinister-imessage-bridge/source/**/*.pyc

# v17 (RKOJ-ELENO 2026-05-23): Sinister Generator source is REAL code (the
# application layer on top of tools/nano-banana/) — not a junction. Track it.
# Per CLAUDE.md "The repo is the Sanctum monorepo — no separate GitHub remote
# (the project lives under Sanctum's tree)". __pycache__ still ignored.
!projects/sinister-generator/source/
!projects/sinister-generator/source/**
projects/sinister-generator/source/**/__pycache__/
projects/sinister-generator/source/**/*.pyc

# Sinister TikTok EMU project root holds its own .git (sister product repo, lane-owned
